items.title: J&J may take a softer tariff hit after US-China pause, CFO says
items.description: Joseph Wolk told an investor conference that the company’s tariff estimate is a “moving target” as trade talks continue with China and Europe and Section 232 investigations are ongoing.

items.title: Johnson & Johnson MedTech introduces automated system for surgical efficiency
